messages.text: Well, how did you get my number? If you're just...someone.
Haha, how are you, Blaire? Had a rough day?
Oh come on... re you trying to be superman? Seriously, who is this?
Not really. Blaire, does it really matter who I am?
Mmmm pretty much, don't ya think? You know my name. I don't know yours.
You could be a serial killer for all I know.
Not a serial killer, just a regular guy that knows you quite well :)
Hahaha it's a bit creepy :p but hey, I heard Peter broke up with you. Are you ok?
Ok...how the hell did you know that?
I told ya, I'm just someone.
This is creepy, you need to stop.
Ok, sorry. I want to cheer you up, will you let me?
Trust me...I'll tell you at the end.
Since you're at the mall atm, mind getting some ice cream?
How do you know that I'm at the mall...OK WAIT. Did Becca ask you to prank me or something?
Cut it off...I don't have time for games.
I don't have time for games either, cupcake. So let's get to it.
Just go buy some ice cream, any favourite flavour in particular? Like...peppermint.
Ok wow, Becca must've freaking told you!
Shh, just go get some ice cream.
Feel any better with that ice cream?
Are you here right now? You are watching this aren't you?
Aw, Blaire. This isn't over yet.
I have plans for you today.
When you're all happy and stuff, I'll reveal myself. Promise ;)
Not making a promise with some...stranger.
No! Blaire, please, come on. Please don't.
What? Gtfo ok, this isn't funny.
I'm having a shitty day and you're only making it worse.
Follow whatever I have planned for you.
Then you'll know who I am.
At the end of the day. I promise! :p
OK, whatever. Let's get this over with.
I want you to come find me.
Haha nope, cupcake. Come find me.
It will lead you to the final destination where I'll reveal myself.
So what's with the ice cream then? Huh?
Idk, just to cheer you up. Ice cream cheers everybody up.
But...I guess it didn't work well for you. Lol.
You're so cute, I kinda missed you.
Ok sooooo, all you have to do is find different notes of different colours.
How am I supposed to find any?
You can find it on the wall, on the ground, etc.
Each note has a place you have to go until you reach the last one.
Is this...like...asking me to work out?
Okk...we're off looking for the first damn clue.
Hey! I've found red and orange. Now I'm in front of a theater.
Have you found the third one yet?
No sign of the third one.
This is a joke, isn't it?
Because you failed. This isn't funny.
Go get water :p We don't want you dying right now.
Aw Blaire. Go look for the yellow note.
Hahaha this is the part that I've been waiting for.
I'm going to take that note.
Tree climbing can be pretty exciting right :p
It can also help you lose some weight.
Don't get me wrong but you can use a little workout, no wrong there.
Wait, I'm on my way to the fourth destination.
Huh, I thought I lost you.
I'm here, now all I have to do is find the green note.
You know what? Brb, let me finish this.
Never thought you would take this long.
Yeah go ahead, keep running. I see you.
I haven't come to notice this...but you have long legs, Blaire.
I'm on my way to the last destination. I've found it all.
I'll meet u there. You better be there.
You better be here! This isn't funny.
Blaire...do you not know me at all?
All the things that you did today...do you not remember?
Peppermint ice cream. Tree climbing. Finding the notes are like treasure hunts aren't they? We used to do that.
Took u awhile but yeah, look up
It really is you. I thought you left.. I missed you
I've always liked you, Blaire. You're my Blaire after all. The things that I asked you to do today...
It wasn't just for fun you know. We did those things before when you were upset and it did cheer you up.
I remember now... omg I can't believe you're here
Come on, stop smiling we have a lot to catch up
